{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-123-124-a-trip-to-australia",
    "title": "Lesson 123: A trip to Australia",
    "audioFilename": "123&124－A Trip to Australia.mp3",
    "duration": 84.95,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.46,
      "end": 2.82,
      "text": "Lesson 123.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第123课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.86,
      "end": 5.98,
      "text": "A Trip to Australia.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "澳大利亚之旅。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 7.62,
      "end": 11.62,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 13,
      "end": 15.32,
      "text": "Who is the man with the beard?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那个留胡子的男人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 17.91,
      "end": 18.73,
      "text": "Look, Scott!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "看，斯科特！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 19.91,
      "end": 25.33,
      "text": "This is a photograph I took during my trip to Australia.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这是我去澳大利亚旅行时拍的一张照片。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.71,
      "end": 28.27,
      "text": "Let me see it, Mike.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "让我看看，迈克。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 29.23,
      "end": 31.21,
      "text": "This is a good photograph.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这张照片拍得真好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 31.83,
      "end": 33.55,
      "text": "Who are these people?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这些人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 34.93,
      "end": 38.03,
      "text": "They're people I met during the trip.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他们是我在旅行途中认识的人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 39.31,
      "end": 41.65,
      "text": "That's the ship we traveled on.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "那就是我们乘坐的船。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 42.49,
      "end": 44.23,
      "text": "What a beautiful ship!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "多漂亮的船啊！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 45.09,
      "end": 45.83,
      "text": "Who's this?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 46.83,
      "end": 50.65,
      "text": "That's the man I told you about, remember?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他就是我跟你提过的那个人，还记得吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 51.49,
      "end": 52.51,
      "text": "Ah, yes.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "啊，记得。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 53.11,
      "end": 56.39,
      "text": "The one who offered you a job in Australia.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "就是那个请你去澳大利亚工作的人。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 57.33,
      "end": 58.13,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "没错。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 58.97,
      "end": 59.75,
      "text": "Who's this?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个人是谁？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 60.55,
      "end": 60.95,
      "text": "Guess.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "猜猜看。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 61.81,
      "end": 63.77,
      "text": "It's not you, is it?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不会是你吧？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 64.13,
      "end": 65.07,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "正是我。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 66.27,
      "end": 72.97,
      "text": "I grew a beard during the trip, but I shaved it off when I came home.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "旅行期间我留了胡子，不过回家后就把它刮掉了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 73.59,
      "end": 75.43,
      "text": "Why did you shave it off?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你为什么把胡子刮掉？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 76.11,
      "end": 78.31,
      "text": "My wife didn't like it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我妻子不喜欢。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
